data.description: Feel right at home in this 3BR/2BA ranch featuring 9ft ceilings & new LVP flooring throughout. The split floor plan allows you privacy in your large MA BR w/ private BA & WIC. 2nd & 3rd BR's are both the perfect size & have ample closet space. Kitchen has newer appliances & lots of counter/cabinet space. Laundry room is oversized & has extra space for storage.  Roof new in 2022. Neighborhood features a pool, clubhouse, park, & walking trails.
